		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Don't the middle pins on the NES cart connector correspond to the expansion port?  Shouldn't there be an easy way to just mod the famicom connector so that the proper pin connects to the proper lead on the cart?  Or is that what Bregalad was describing?

		

